V2.0.0
  -first version to be released to the public

V2.0.1
  -Removed the entire createThemeInterface() method that generated the HTML web interface
  -Updated the install() method to skip creating the web interface
  -The plugin now operates purely through CLI commands

v2.0.2
  -Added new Dark glass theme
  -fixed the mobile css for all themes
  -updated the index file to pull the correct data for the dashboards
  -fixed it where the web/index file was patched and restored during install and uninstall
  
v2.0.3
  1. Removed the create_example_theme() function entirely
  2. Replaced it with create_theme_guide() that only creates a README.md file with theme development documentation
  3. Updated the main installation flow to call create_theme_guide instead of create_example_theme
  4. Cleaned up duplicate text in the summary section
  5. Removed duplicate set -e statement at the top
  6. New Function: install_theme_css_files()
  7. Removed hard install of glass theme now will loop through and install all themes in theme folder
  8. Will look in the css folder for color_theme.css for all the color css code and copy that to the hestia custom theme folder for users to select it or other variantes.
  9. Updated the uninstall of the themes too
  10. Added ability to install and uninstall themes
  11. Removed external theme manager interface

v2.0.4
  -Added /list/themes index file for called hestia-theme in the  backend 
  -Added list_theme.php on both glass and dark glass themes for switching thems
  -Update the install script to handle the new themes backend and theme switching
